HEADWORD: Philatelist
<hw>Phi*lat"e*list</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One versed in
philately; one who collects postage stamps, as a hobby or for
investment; a stamp collector.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

